snippet.title: Pokémon Platinum Version - US Commercial [English]
snippet.description: Pokémon Platinum Version introduces you to a new world to explore in the Sinnoh region: the Distortion World. While Pokémon Diamond Version mainly featured Dialga, and Palkia played a key role in the Pokémon Pearl Version, Pokémon Platinum Version tells the epic story of Giratina and the new Distortion World.
